import React from 'react'
import {Form} from 'react-bootstrap'

const switchTo = () => {
  return (
    <Form>
  <Form.Check 
    type="switch"
    id="custom-switch"
    label="Check this switch"
  />
  <Form.Check 
    disabled
    type="switch"
    label="disabled switch"
    id="disabled-custom-switch"
  />
</Form>
  )
}

export default switchTo
